# Hitpoint AU Official Website — Cursor Rules
# Source: https://github.com/ashc0815/au_officialweb
# Deployed: https://auofficialweb.vercel.app

## Project Overview
Static HTML/CSS website for Hitpoint Solution AU — an SAP Concur implementation and governance partner for ANZ markets.
Target audience: CFOs, Finance Directors, and procurement leads at mid-market Australian companies.
No build system. No npm. No framework. Pure HTML5 + CSS3 + minimal vanilla JS.

## Tech Stack
- Pure static HTML5 + CSS3
- Google Fonts: DM Sans (weights 400/500/600/700, ital, opsz 9..40)
- Single global stylesheet: css/styles.css
- CSS custom properties used throughout (e.g. var(--bg-soft))
- Vanilla JS only — inline <script> at bottom of each page (nav toggle + year)
- Salesforce Web-to-Lead on contact.html
- Deployed on Vercel (auofficialweb.vercel.app)

