## Nav Rules
- 7 items exactly as shown above — do not add or remove items
- "Start with a Governance Snapshot" was intentionally removed as a nav item — do NOT re-add it
- If you find it still present in any page (e.g. index.html), remove it
- The Governance Snapshot CTA belongs in the hero section as .btn-primary, not in nav

## Homepage Card Grid Pattern
Issue pages are surfaced via .card-grid in index.html:
```html
<a href="PAGE.html" class="card">
  <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">EMOJI</div>
  <h3>TITLE</h3>
  <div class="card-desc"><ul><li>...</li></ul></div>
  <span class="card-cta">Explore X →</span>
</a>
```
The four cards link to: audit-readiness.html, fbt-eofy.html, eofy-control-drift.html, china-invoice-compliance.html

